==Document "Aeternalis Flos Noctis." December 17, 2024.==


The faction known as "Aeternalis Flos Noctis" is causing serious problems within this place. The religious group has grown seriously and now has approximately more than 40 members.

All members of this group are extremely aggressive towards anyone who refuses to adhere to their religion. To date, 23 deaths have been confirmed. In the current level situation, we are unable to try to help refugees and those persecuted by the group. The exposure of the entire place to radiation is lethal for us, and all current posts and communities created were destroyed by the faction.

Those people can no longer be called people. They act like creatures, torturing to death those who refuse to join the faction. I don't know what's happening. They destroyed all of our communities and killed many.

At this point, we no longer know what to do. Any help is useless, the radiation is lethal, and no one is capable of fighting. They don't get tired? They do not have sickness? The radiation doesn't seem to affect them anymore. 

The worst of all is that we know nothing, absolutely NOTHING, about who these people were, are, or what they really want. One of our members tried to enter this faction and then said he would come back to us with information, but he never came back to us, and we never saw him again.

We no longer have a choice. Anyone who enters here and wants to survive must surrender. I lost everything I had, WE lost it. There is no other option.

-Unknown.

</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

